{"TopicId":134345,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"A.I. pilot flying VTOL (BDArmor)","CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T21:40:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T21:40:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I was wondering if the A.I. pilot could fly a VTOL.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was amazed it could fly and land easily with the vtol engine alone ! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022f3A9W9r.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/f3A9W9r.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d4v4b2F.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/d4v4b2F.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid anybody else try this ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit, I had to switch the engines manualy, AI pilot can\u0027t do that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-17T01:25:13Z\u0022 title=\u002203/17/2016 01:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Triop\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T21:47:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload for that VTOL plane?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T22:40:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-i